{"tid":193293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[端傳媒] 何潔泓，被運動消費的美麗~","createTime":"2017-04-09T08:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T09:05:09.000Z","uid":49388,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd422c8562922c14c29e956cf9b81822401b2acf","tid":193293,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T08:02:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/40204b6a81d14da08b961a57009cb5e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2F40204b6a81d14da08b961a57009cb5e8.jpg&h=6fc05f3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n攝影師從攝影機中看着何潔泓的臉，拍攝過無數人的他仍然忍不住說：「長得真好看。」<br />\n<br />\n她是天生巴掌臉，輪廓分明，骨架纖細，真人看其實消瘦，可是在拉闊了的屏幕中又剛剛好，與生俱來適合上鏡。不參與社運行動時，她常穿古著風的連身花裙。拍攝時，她會專門問攝影師可否拍左臉，抱怨別的媒體把她拍得太黝黑。<br />\n<br />\n24歲的何潔泓是香港嶺南大學哲學畢業生，中學開始參與社會運動，反過高鐵興建、守過菜園村、聲援過罷工的碼頭工人，因為生得漂亮，在圈中有「社運女神」之稱。而在雨傘運動期間，她的社運生涯卻從光環之上一路跌落谷底。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n佔領運動的第一個星期，她與朋友去旺角佔領區走走看看。在匯豐銀行，她看到幾個大學同學把守住一個新的『大台』，她說聽到熱血公民的人正熱烈喊口號。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20150923-hongkong-umbrellamovementtrauma/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20150923-hongkong-umbrellamovementtrauma%2F&d=AthmRk%2BBSDjaWf6zT95BzGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=fb7809e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20150923-hongkong-umbrellamovementtrauma/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vignette2.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/d/df/846d2ca624eaeec2ad7c776e75aac3ed-3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette2.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fd%2Fdf%2F846d2ca624eaeec2ad7c776e75aac3ed-3.png&h=4b8f1d41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟誰是誰非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5787487b0d675533724004c06e412af2718d95b4","tid":193293,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T08:03:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3ab8c18aedba2f902a649fefbcba07f112dadc","tid":193293,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T08:05:25.000Z","msg":"丁死連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d767da1a86119d1104bdc14b9cfbf1ba8d0f1b","tid":193293,"uid":21008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T08:05:34.000Z","msg":"個家姐定阿妹叫小明，仔都生埋"},{"pid":"56205c9a81f6aff1b116e2fb074aa183b0a36a77","tid":193293,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T08:20:20.000Z","msg":"唔係就執啦咩?"},{"pid":"ec005cf34759a13f60f5451fa1db48e7e9a77c9e","tid":193293,"uid":5603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T08:20:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個家姐定阿妹叫小明，仔都生埋</blockquote><br />\n佢係家姐 小明係妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63152ecdb15e425fef3c8757f7893bbb27ac335d","tid":193293,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T09:05:09.000Z","msg":"左膠公厠"}]}